---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import heroProfiles from "../assets/images/hero-profiles.png";
---

<section id="hero" class="relative overflow-hidden px-6 pb-24 pt-24">
	<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_65%_55%_at_50%_-5%,rgba(168,85,247,.24),transparent)]"></div>
	<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,rgba(255,255,255,.035)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,rgba(255,255,255,.035)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:56px_56px] [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_70%_60%_at_50%_0%,black,transparent)]"></div>

	<div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_.95fr]">
		<div data-reveal>
			<div class="mb-7 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-emerald-300/20 bg-emerald-300/[.07] px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-200">
				<span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-300"></span>
				Open source, nacido en Latinoamérica
			</div>
			<h1 class="max-w-3xl text-5xl font-extrabold leading-[1.02] tracking-[-.045em] text-white sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
				Tu GitHub cuenta una historia. <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-300 via-cyan-300 to-fuchsia-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Haz que se vea.</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="mt-7 max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
				repo.lat convierte el trabajo que ya haces en un perfil propio: proyectos, lenguajes y actividad, con HTML y CSS que puedes cambiar a tu manera.
			</p>
			<div class="mt-9 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
				<a href="#conectar" class="magnetic-btn ripple rounded-full bg-white px-7 py-3.5 text-center text-sm font-bold text-[#0a0a12] transition hover:bg-emerald-200">Quiero crear mi perfil</a>
				<a href="#perfiles" class="magnetic-btn rounded-full border border-white/15 px-7 py-3.5 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-white/5">Ver perfiles de ejemplo</a>
			</div>
			<p class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-500">Gratis, auditable y sin pedir acceso de escritura.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="relative min-h-[390px]" data-reveal>
			<div class="absolute inset-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-400/20 to-fuchsia-500/20 blur-3xl"></div>
			<Image
				src={heroProfiles}
				alt="Tarjetas de perfiles de desarrollo en tres dimensiones"
				class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[620px] drop-shadow-[0_30px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,.45)]"
				width={620}
				loading="eager"
			/>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
